      skos:note "Scarlet frames the landing page with the same structure as a memory itself: primary source material (what is actually happening) plus commentary and framing (briefly). The product's own epistemics become the page's IA. This is a new application of the content/commentary split principle (narr:Narrative_ContentCommentarySplit) to the marketing surface." ;
